a2t.text_actual: Music for your eyes.  Vevo offers the largest collection of premium official music videos. Start watching your favorite music videos and catch daily video premieres by downloading Vevo for Android today.  Discover what’s happening in the world through music. Quickly access what’s worth checking out, even if it’s not on your radar. Stream exciting new music videos, original shows, and live music performances from your favorite artists for free.  Make playlists of your favorite pop, rock, rap, electronic, R&B, and country music videos. See a video you like? Add it to a playlist. Let your friends know what you’re streaming by sharing your favorite music videos by sharing to your favorite social networks like Facebook and Twitter. Not sure what to listen to? Vevo recommends music videos while you’re watching based on your personal tastes. We'll scan your music library and provide recommendations for videos that we know you’ll like.    Take a deeper dive into music discovery, where you can explore different genres, activities and channels created by our music insiders. A mix of channels and playlists are ready and waiting just for you. Or just sit back and relax with Vevo TV, a hand-curated music video channel. Turn it on and enjoy an HD music experience that features everything from daily premieres to live music to the best classics. New Features:   -  New design  -  Realtime Feed   -  Music Matching  -  Improved browsing, video recommendations, search & player  -  Performance enhancements Be sure to join the Vevo community to discover & share your favorite music. Facebook -  https://www.facebook.com/vevo  Twitter -  https://twitter.com/vevo  Tumblr -  http://vevo.tumblr.com/  Instagram -  http://instagram.com/vevo  Pinterest -  http://www.pinterest.com/vevomusic   PLEASE NOTE: Vevo will work over cellular (3G or LTE) network connections, but for the highest quality music video experience, we suggest accessing via Wi-Fi whenever possible. Due to the nature of some licenses from the content owners, features and videos may not be available in all regions.
